comment.narrative:
Advocacy for policy and legal reforms were identified as a key sustainability measure. In collaboration with the civil society entities from Kwale, the project identified the Kwale County Integrated Development Plan 2023-2027 development process, Kwale County Programme Based Budget for FY 2023-2024, and the Kwale County SGBV Bill 2018 as key opportunities for joint advocacy. These outcomes are likely to greatly contribute to sustainability.

The project has also continued to strengthen the capacity of GYW advocates and community activists on GYW Led advocacy.

The Project is also working with other civil society entities, media agencies, community members and influential community leaders to advocate for GYW issues.;
